#: ../../S/Stone-Age.rst:25
msgid ""
"More generally, a pejorative for any crufty, ancient piece of hardware or "
"software technology. Note that this is used even by people who were there "
"for the :ref:`Stone-Age` (sense 1)."
msgstr ""
"より一般的には、古臭く時代遅れのハードウェアやソフトウェア技術に対する蔑称。これは\\ :ref:`Stone-Age`\\ "
"(語義1)を実際に経験した人々ですら使うことに注意。"
